String","label":"Special","value":"<p>The mooks created by each level of the bones beneath appear in the Summoned Creatures compendium. The level or physical nature of the mooks is irrelevant; the magic of the spell turns whatever creatures it’s forced to work with into skeletal mook allies with the listed stats.</p><p>The new mooks take their turn immediately after your turn.</p><p>It’s worth mentioning that the mooks created by this spell don’t count as summoned mooks. This isn’t a summoning spell.</p>"},"effect":{"type":"String","label":"Effect","value":""},"spellLevel3":{"type":"String","label":"3rd Level Spell","value":""},"spellLevel5":{"type":"String","label":"5th Level Spell","value":"[[7d12+@int.dmg+@atk.a.bonus]] negative energy damage."},"spellLevel7":{"type":"String","label":"7th Level Spell","value":"[[(2d6)*10+@int.dmg+@atk.a.bonus]] negative energy damage."},"spellLevel9":{"type":"String","label":"9th Level Spell","value":"[[(2d10)*10+@int.dmg+@atk.a.bonus]] negative energy damage."},"spellChain":{"type":"String","label":"Chain Spell","value":""},"breathWeapon":{"type":"String","label":"Breath Weapon","value":""},"recharge":{"type":"Number","label":"Recharge","value":0},"quantity":{"type":"Number","label":"Uses","value":1},"maxQuantity":{"type":"Number","label":"Uses","value":1},"feats":{"adventurer":{"description":{"type":"String","label":"Adventurer Feat","value":""},"isActive":{"type":"Boolean","label":"Active","value":false}},"champion":{"description":{"type":"String","label":"Champion Feat","value":""},"isActive":{"type":"Boolean","label":"Active","value":false}},"epic":{"description":{"type":"String","label":"Epic Feat","value":""},"isActive":{"type":"Boolean","label":"Active","value":false}}}},"flags":{},"img":"systems/archmage/assets/icons/skills/red_28.jpg","_id":"qhKOMgSBfO2vVLgf"}
